  <title>lp_solve-&lp_solve-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This packages provides a development library and a program which solves
      linear programming (LP), integer linear programming (ILP), and mixed
      integer linear programming (MILP) problems.
    </para>

