  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install lp_solve by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>cd lpsolve55 &amp;&amp;
sh ccc &amp;&amp;
cd ../lp_solve &amp;&amp;
sh ccc &amp;&amp;
cd ..</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>install -v -m 755 lp_solve/bin/ux*/lp_solve /usr/bin &amp;&amp;
install -v -m 755 lpsolve55/bin/ux*/liblpsolve55.so /usr/lib &amp;&amp;
mkdir -v /usr/include/lpsolve &amp;&amp;
install -v -m 644 lp*.h /usr/include/lpsolve</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

